        <td>
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small">Pitch-Circle Diameter (PCD)</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The effective diameter of a Belt as it passes around a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Pulley</text>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The <text styleclass="Parameter-Popup">Number-of-Teeth</text> (see <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Pulley dialog</text>) and the <text styleclass="Parameter-Popup">Tooth-Pitch</text> (see <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Motion-Path dialog</text>) control the <text styleclass="VariableName-small">PCD</text>.</para>
          <para styleclass="VariableName-small">Tooth-Pitch<text styleclass="Popup Box">:</text></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The Linear distance between adjacent teeth.</para>
        </td>
